**4.2 ShipmentBlockSource (NEW in v1.1)**

Tracks which blocks contributed how many kg to each truck. Replaces
BARLAG spreadsheet.

+-----------------------------------------------------------------------+
| class ShipmentBlockSource(models.Model):                              |
|                                                                       |
| shipment = models.ForeignKey(Shipment,                                |
| related_name=\'block_sources\', on_delete=CASCADE)                    |
|                                                                       |
| block = models.ForeignKey(GreenhouseBlock, on_delete=PROTECT)         |
|                                                                       |
| weight_kg = models.DecimalField(max_digits=10, decimal_places=2)      |
|                                                                       |
| class Meta:                                                           |
|                                                                       |
| unique_together = \[\'shipment\', \'block\'\]                         |
|                                                                       |
| \# Validation: sum of all block_sources.weight_kg ==                  |
| shipment.weight_net_kg                                                |
|                                                                       |
| \# Soltanmyrat fills this when loading truck                          |
|                                                                       |
| \# Example: Truck 02FB005/26 = B:12,371 + C:6,032 = 18,403 total      |
+-----------------------------------------------------------------------+

