**4.6 Model: WeeklyHarvestPlan (NEW in v1.1)**

Replicates the Hepdelik planlama grid. 15 blocks × 6 days per week.

+-----------------------------------------------------------------------+
| class WeeklyHarvestPlan(models.Model):                                |
|                                                                       |
| week_number = models.IntegerField() \# ISO week: 40, 41, 42\...       |
|                                                                       |
| year = models.IntegerField()                                          |
|                                                                       |
| block = models.ForeignKey(GreenhouseBlock, on_delete=CASCADE)         |
|                                                                       |
| monday_kg = models.DecimalField(max_digits=10, decimal_places=2,      |
| default=0)                                                            |
|                                                                       |
| tuesday_kg = models.DecimalField(max_digits=10, decimal_places=2,     |
| default=0)                                                            |
|                                                                       |
| wednesday_kg = models.DecimalField(max_digits=10, decimal_places=2,   |
| default=0)                                                            |
|                                                                       |
| thursday_kg = models.DecimalField(max_digits=10, decimal_places=2,    |
| default=0)                                                            |
|                                                                       |
| friday_kg = models.DecimalField(max_digits=10, decimal_places=2,      |
| default=0)                                                            |
|                                                                       |
| saturday_kg = models.DecimalField(max_digits=10, decimal_places=2,    |
| default=0)                                                            |
|                                                                       |
| actual_total_kg = models.DecimalField(max_digits=10,                  |
| decimal_places=2, null=True)                                          |
|                                                                       |
| class Meta:                                                           |
|                                                                       |
| unique_together = \[\'week_number\', \'year\', \'block\'\]            |
|                                                                       |
| \@property                                                            |
|                                                                       |
| def planned_total_kg(self):                                           |
|                                                                       |
| return sum(\[self.monday_kg, self.tuesday_kg, self.wednesday_kg,      |
|                                                                       |
| self.thursday_kg, self.friday_kg, self.saturday_kg\])                 |
|                                                                       |
| \@property                                                            |
|                                                                       |
| def variance_kg(self):                                                |
|                                                                       |
| if self.actual_total_kg is None: return None                          |
|                                                                       |
| return self.actual_total_kg - self.planned_total_kg                   |
|                                                                       |
| \# \~24 weeks per season × 15 blocks = 360 rows/season                |
|                                                                       |
| \# Planned by block managers on Friday                                |
|                                                                       |
| \# Actual filled on Saturday                                          |
+-----------------------------------------------------------------------+

**5. API Endpoints per Sprint**

**5.1 Sprint 1 (Weeks 1--3): Foundation + Data Import**

  -------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
  **Method**   **Endpoint**                   **Purpose**
  ------------ ------------------------------ -----------------------------------------
  GET          /api/shipments/                List with filters: status, date, country,
                                              firm, customer, block

  POST         /api/shipments/                Create new shipment

  GET/PATCH    /api/shipments/{id}/           Detail + update (role-based field access)

  POST         /api/shipments/import-excel/   Import 983 rows from main Excel

  GET          /api/shipments/stats/          Dashboard: counts by status, tonnage,
                                              revenue

  GET          /api/greenhouse-blocks/        List 15 blocks with manager, variety,
                                              area

  GET          /api/export-firms/             List 24 firms

  GET          /api/import-firms/             List 111 buyers with search

  GET          /api/customers/                List \~15 customers
  -------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

**5.2 Sprint 2 (Weeks 4--6): Lifecycle + Firms + \$10K + Block Sources**

  -----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
  **Method**   **Endpoint**                         **Purpose**
  ------------ ------------------------------------ ---------------------------------------
  POST         /api/shipments/{id}/advance/         Move to next status step (validates
                                                    role)

  POST         /api/shipments/{id}/firm-splits/     Add/update firm split with \$10K
                                                    warning

  POST         /api/shipments/{id}/block-sources/   NEW: Record which blocks contributed kg

