**7. Business Rules --- Implementation Spec**

**BR1: Standard Truck Weight**

+-----------------------------------------------------------------------+
| STANDARD_GROSS_KG = 20500                                             |
|                                                                       |
| STANDARD_NET_KG = 18100                                               |
|                                                                       |
| STANDARD_PACKAGING_KG = 2400                                          |
|                                                                       |
| \# Warn if gross \> 21000 or net \< 15000. Do NOT block.              |
+-----------------------------------------------------------------------+

**BR2: Truck Threshold (NEW in v1.1)**

+-----------------------------------------------------------------------+
| \# From Hepdelik planlama: 18,500 kg = 1 export truck                 |
|                                                                       |
| TRUCK_THRESHOLD_KG = 18500                                            |
|                                                                       |
| def daily_truck_count(total_harvest_kg):                              |
|                                                                       |
| return total_harvest_kg / TRUCK_THRESHOLD_KG                          |
|                                                                       |
| \# Show on dashboard: \'Today: \~4.5 trucks available\'               |
|                                                                       |
| \# Gadam decides split: 2 KZ + 2 RU + 0 Gapy                          |
+-----------------------------------------------------------------------+

**BR3: Shipment Code Format**

+-----------------------------------------------------------------------+
| \# Format: DDMM+seq/YY e.g. 02FB005/26                                |
|                                                                       |
| \# DD = day (02), MM = month abbreviation (FB=Feb, MR=Mar), seq =     |
| 3-digit, YY = year                                                    |
|                                                                       |
| \# Month codes from BARLAG: FB=February, MR=March (confirm others     |
| with Gadam)                                                           |
|                                                                       |
| MONTH_CODES = {\'01\':\'YN\', \'02\':\'FB\', \'03\':\'MR\',           |
| \'04\':\'AP\', \'05\':\'MY\', \'06\':\'IY\',                          |
|                                                                       |
| \'09\':\'SN\', \'10\':\'OK\', \'11\':\'NY\', \'12\':\'DK\'}           |
+-----------------------------------------------------------------------+

**BR4: \$10K Rule**

+-----------------------------------------------------------------------+
| WARN_THRESHOLD_USD = 9000 \# Yellow warning                           |
|                                                                       |
| BLOCK_THRESHOLD_USD = 10000 \# Red warning (does NOT block)           |
|                                                                       |
| \# Calculate from: weight_kg \* price_per_kg per firm in split        |
|                                                                       |
| \# Display real-time as user adjusts weight split                     |
+-----------------------------------------------------------------------+

**BR5: Quota 1:10 Ratio**

+-----------------------------------------------------------------------+
| QUOTA_RATIO = 10                                                      |
|                                                                       |
| \# Source: DomesticSale records (from Birlesme pomidor kwota sheet)   |
|                                                                       |
| \# Season example: 1,564,252 kg domestic = 15,642,520 kg export quota |
|                                                                       |
| \# Alert at 80%, 90%, 95%. Soft block at 100%.                        |
+-----------------------------------------------------------------------+

**BR6: Block Source Validation (NEW in v1.1)**

+-----------------------------------------------------------------------+
| \# When Soltanmyrat records block sources for a shipment:             |
|                                                                       |
| \# sum(block_source.weight_kg) MUST == shipment.weight_net_kg         |
|                                                                       |
| \# Each block_source.weight_kg \> 0                                   |
|                                                                       |
| \# Each block must be a valid GreenhouseBlock (one of 15)             |
|                                                                       |
| \# A truck can source from 1-5 blocks (typical: 1-3)                  |
+-----------------------------------------------------------------------+

**BR7: Missing Report Enforcement**

+-----------------------------------------------------------------------+
| \# Cannot move to \'tamamlandy\' without SalesReport                  |
|                                                                       |
| \# Auto-alert: if ts_satyldy \> 3 days and no report → Telegram       |
| reminder                                                              |
|                                                                       |
| \# After 7 days: escalate to Gadam                                    |
+-----------------------------------------------------------------------+

**BR8: Multi-Firm Split**

+-----------------------------------------------------------------------+
| MAX_FIRMS_PER_SHIPMENT = 3                                            |
|                                                                       |
| \# 2-firm split: common (35.6%), 3-firm: rare                         |
|                                                                       |
| \# Each firm = separate CMR + invoice                                 |
|                                                                       |
| \# sum(firm_split.weight_kg) == shipment.weight_net_kg                |
+-----------------------------------------------------------------------+

**BR9: Weekly Planning Cycle (NEW in v1.1)**

+-----------------------------------------------------------------------+
| \# Friday: Block managers enter planned kg for next week (Mon-Sat per |
| block)                                                                |
|                                                                       |
| \# Daily: Update actual harvest                                       |
|                                                                       |
| \# Saturday: Compare plan vs actual, variance report                  |
|                                                                       |
| \# Planning feeds truck forecast: total_planned / 18,500 = trucks     |
| needed                                                                |
|                                                                       |
| \# Gadam uses truck forecast to pre-arrange transport                 |
+-----------------------------------------------------------------------+

