**11.1 MSSQL Workarounds**

  -----------------------------------------------------------------------
  **Constraint**         **Workaround**
  ---------------------- ------------------------------------------------
  No JSONField           Separate model fields or related tables

  No DISTINCT ON         ROW_NUMBER() window function

  2,100 parameter limit  bulk_create(batch_size=500)

  Turkmen/Russian text   Cyrillic_General_CI_AS + Latin_General_CI_AS
                         collation
