**13. Conclusion**

  -----------------------------------------------------------------------
  **P3 Export now has 10 models, 35+ API endpoints, 17 screens, 9
  business rules, and real reference data for all 15 blocks, 24 firms,
  111 buyers, and 15 domestic purchasers.** Pomidor Dükany analysis
  resolved 5 of 14 gaps and revealed 3 new models (GreenhouseBlock,
  ShipmentBlockSource, DomesticBuyer) plus the critical planning→export
  bridge. **Only 9 gaps remain, all LOW-MEDIUM risk and resolvable in
  Sprint 1--2. Start development now.**

